# Results

This folder holds the real output of running `src/evaluate.py` (via the
Colab notebook):

- `metrics_before.json` — zero-shot base model scores on the held-out test set
- `metrics_after.json` — LoRA fine-tuned model scores on the same test set
- `comparison.png` — bar chart comparing the two 
- `sample_outputs.md` — a handful of real before/after example predictions (add your downloaded copy here)

See the main README's "Results" section for the full write-up and the
round-1-vs-round-2 comparison.
